{"tid":2426080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"擅tag用戶照　Facebook賠50億和解","createTime":"2021-02-27T18:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T00:29:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2faba3a95ad6c2b998376429bb838746695b63","tid":2426080,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T18:57:06.000Z","msg":"美國一名聯邦法官前天批准facebook以6.5億美元（50.7億港元）和解一宗集體訴訟，案件涉fb未經用戶同意，用人臉識別技術在照片加標籤，法官指這是其中一宗最大金額和解的侵犯私隱案。<br />\n<br />\n案件在2015年在伊利諾州提出，後轉到fb總部所在的加州集體訴訟，共有160萬伊利諾州用戶索賠。該州的《生物識別數據私隱法》，容許消費者控告未得他們批准蒐集其臉孔和指紋等數據的公司，原告指fb未徵求他們准許，使用人臉識別技術掃瞄用戶上載的照片，並把人臉數據儲存，為照片上人臉加標籤。<br />\n<br />\n加州北區聯邦地方法官多納托在批准和解書上表示，和解方案「將令每一位想要補償的集體訴訟者，至少得到345美元（2,691港元）」，形容是「消費者在爭論激烈的數碼私隱方面的重大勝利」。<br />\n<br />\nfb指：「我們欣慰可達成和解，無論對我們的社群和股東，都最符合他們的利益。」朱克伯格創辦的fb被控告後，已修改照片標籤系統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210228/3SEJVOX7L5DDBNHI3CXVZOYQUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210228%2F3SEJVOX7L5DDBNHI3CXVZOYQUU%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3kXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=a9c290e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210228%2F3SEJVOX7L5DDBNHI3CXVZOYQUU%2F&h=220efa19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210228/3SEJVOX7L5DDBNHI3CXVZOYQUU/</a>"},{"pid":"48f62ea5b5d78d9573783b01b72c63ae44fdc9c7","tid":2426080,"uid":83102,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T19:02:09.000Z","msg":"將令每一位想要補償的集體訴訟者，至少得到345美元（2,691港元）<br />\n<br />\n非美帝/加州人可唔可以申請補償<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ad3961bc63009b9d89d83e825b7f222cb18fce","tid":2426080,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f62ea5b5d78d9573783b01b72c63ae44fdc9c7","tid":2426080,"uid":83102,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T19:02:09.000Z","msg":"將令每一位想要補償的集體訴訟者，至少得到345美元（2,691港元）<br />\n<br />\n非美帝/加州人可唔可以申請補償<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"a2941e0974fdd2cecb82e929f851916584d5dee1","tid":2426080,"uid":76902,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48f62ea5b5d78d9573783b01b72c63ae44fdc9c7","tid":2426080,"uid":83102,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T19:02:09.000Z","msg":"將令每一位想要補償的集體訴訟者，至少得到345美元（2,691港元）<br />\n<br />\n非美帝/加州人可唔可以申請補償<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T19:15:21.000Z","msg":"唔得<br />\n住美國仲要係 Illinois個州先得"},{"pid":"e56ea7f76afffff60f428bc5f6ceddb0108ce884","tid":2426080,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T00:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d140f3cfa77f6cf18d01c470c9d8e74f59cf0a","tid":2426080,"uid":383344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e56ea7f76afffff60f428bc5f6ceddb0108ce884","tid":2426080,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T00:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T00:29:11.000Z","msg":"bot<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}